data.description: Victorian home with a grand front porch & pillars. This home features unbelievable space- extra large living room, dining room, foyer & bedrooms. True to the style of home, there is a great open staircase, plus a back set of stairs, as well as a fireplace, detailed woodwork, hardwood floors, and awesome walk-up attic. The kitchen has been updated, with cherry cabinets and granite counters. New roof in 2020, 2 car detached garage with alley access. The exterior does need some updates, but it is a diamond in the rough! Great location within walking distance to downtown, hospital & river front. Don't miss the opportunity to make this home your dream home!
